				<td colspan="2"><span>Is there anything I can increase so I can go from twisting 3 to 4 songs?  I see where a few comments have come in and said that they can twist 4 songs and just wondered how?  My twisting ability is great for 3, and I try to do 4 and 5 but I end up losing a few of the effects that were first cast.  Any suggestions or am I just stuck being a three stringed bard???
